{"tid":2044294,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【司長網誌】陳茂波：我可以肯定的說 國安法不影響聯滙及資金進出","createTime":"2020-05-31T04:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T05:12:22.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"257a99bf44e2e19d5e19cd094dc224d0ded422a3","tid":2044294,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://thumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub/KZ0B1YqgrnBUBW-hGVPhrjDZBKI=/arc-photo-appledaily/ap-ne-1-prod/public/2ZMFK4OYR7KZ4V6ORFWSTKMY5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub%2FKZ0B1YqgrnBUBW-hGVPhrjDZBKI%3D%2Farc-photo-appledaily%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F2ZMFK4OYR7KZ4V6ORFWSTKMY5M.jpg&h=2175ca49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人大會議通過「港版國安法」，並授權人大常委會進行相關的法律制訂工作，引發社會討論。財政司長陳茂波網誌提到，知悉市場關注本港資金自由進出、聯繫匯率制度運作，及香港國際金融中心地位的未來，強調「我可以肯定的說，這些都不受影響」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200531/DKFDOZQTKLEOYKCTA2SLP75S3A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200531%2FDKFDOZQTKLEOYKCTA2SLP75S3A%2F&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=b2b85dfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200531%2FDKFDOZQTKLEOYKCTA2SLP75S3A%2F&h=112dcd8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200531/DKFDOZQTKLEOYKCTA2SLP75S3A/</a>"},{"pid":"91b6836197f8677e1e3c32f221d31d0a74a51e37","tid":2044294,"uid":9435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"257a99bf44e2e19d5e19cd094dc224d0ded422a3","tid":2044294,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://thumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub/KZ0B1YqgrnBUBW-hGVPhrjDZBKI=/arc-photo-appledaily/ap-ne-1-prod/public/2ZMFK4OYR7KZ4V6ORFWSTKMY5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub%2FKZ0B1YqgrnBUBW-hGVP